---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Admin"
  description="The Trace Manifest administration dashboard."
>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Admin</h1>
    <p class="meta" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
      Administration dashboard for source management, ingestion monitoring, and editorial review.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid--3">
      <a href="/admin/sources" class="card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
        <h2 style="font-size:1.15rem;">Sources</h2>
        <p class="meta" style="margin-top:0.5rem;">Manage 64 sources across 3 tiers. View health status, trigger manual fetches, pause or remove sources.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;color:var(--color-accent);">Manage sources →</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/admin/jobs" class="card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
        <h2 style="font-size:1.15rem;">Ingestion Jobs</h2>
        <p class="meta" style="margin-top:0.5rem;">Monitor scheduled and manual ingestion jobs. View success rates, item counts, and error logs.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;color:var(--color-accent);">View jobs →</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/admin/review" class="card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
        <h2 style="font-size:1.15rem;">Review Queue</h2>
        <p class="meta" style="margin-top:0.5rem;">Items flagged for human review per ADR-0004. Approve, edit, or reject before publication.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;color:var(--color-accent);">Open queue →</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <section style="margin-top:3rem;padding:1rem;background:var(--surface-2);border-radius:var(--radius);">
      <h2>Phase 3 Status</h2>
      <div style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
        <p class="meta"><strong>Pipeline:</strong> 64 sources → ingestion (every 30 min) → classification (16 topics, lexical) → cross-source matching (Jaccard) → story clustering → claim extraction → conflict detection → human review → publication.</p>
        <p class="meta"><strong>Worker:</strong> <code>trace-manifest-ingestion.philgeran.workers.dev</code> with 5 cron triggers. D1 database (16 tables + pipeline_stages). 138 items ingested.</p>
        <p class="meta"><strong>Completed:</strong> Classification, cross-source matching, semantic dedup, story clustering, claim extraction (10 claim classes), conflict detection, evidence labelling (10-state system), rating explanation panel.</p>
        <p class="meta"><strong>Next:</strong> Correction workflow, knowledge base (Phase 3B), golden evaluation dataset expansion.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
